#id=1
#text=Last night I realized I did not have anything for dinner .
#id=2
#text=To solve this conundrum I first thought about ordering out food .
#id=3
#text=This , I realized , was too expensive as I am a broke college graduate just trying to get by .
#id=4
#text=I settled on an alternative , going to the grocery store to purchase food .
#id=5
#text=I walked down the street from my apartment to the Whole Foods in the brisk spring air .
#id=6
#text=I was on a mission , purchase delicious food .
#id=7
#text=When I reached the Whole Foods , the distinct smell of smug filled my nostrils .
#id=8
#text=Organic , natural , non deoderized humans paced to and fro within the confines of the kale infused shelving units .
#id=9
#text=I quickly scuttled to the small frozen foods section to purchase some ` healthy ' junk food .
#text=I selected chicken tenders and a small frozen pizza .
#text=Skirting the weed smoking hippies throughout the store I returned to the front .
#text=I quickly made my purchase and sprinted back towards home to concoct my wonderfully delicious tendies and pizza .
